# Please write your commit messages according to the following specifications 

# <type>[optional scope]: <description>
# break line
# [optional body]
# break line
# [optional footer(s)]

# ======================================
# Type should be one of the following:
# ======================================
#   * build      构建相关代码和文件
#   * chore      构建过程或者辅助工具的变动
#   * ci         CI or CD
#   * docs       文档相关变动
#   * feat       新功能特性
#   * fix        修复
#   * perf       优化,性能提升
#   * refactor   重构
#   * revert     回滚
#   * style      代码样式或者格式化代码
#   * test       测试
#   * merge      合并
#   * sync       同步

# 如果是破坏性的改动,必须加上!,并且在footer加上BREAKING CHANGE:

# ======================================
# Scope:
# ======================================
# scope就是影响范围
# 比如: compile, build, *, view, service
# 根据业务和项目自己把握,能用来区分层次


# ======================================
# Description:
# ======================================
# 字数不要超过80
# 首字母小写
# 第一个是一个动词
# 不要句号

# ======================================
# Description:
# ======================================


# ======================================
# Examples
# ======================================

# feat(*): add library for tailwind
# 
# install development libraries by npm install
#   - postcss
#   - postcss-cli
#   - autoprefixer
#   - @snowpack/plugin-postcss
